wide_layout: true
---

<h1>Umræðan</h1>
<p>Yfirferð á einstökum greinum og yfirlýsingum í ESB-umræðunni, þar sem hvert atriði er borið saman við gögn og heimildir.</p>

{% if reports | length %}
<div class="reports-grid">
  {% for report in reports | reverse %}
  <a href="/umraedan/{{ report.slug }}/" class="report-card">
    <div class="report-card-header">
      <h3 class="report-card-title">{{ report.article_title }}</h3>
      <time datetime="{{ report.analysis_date }}">{{ report.analysis_date | isDate }}</time>
    </div>
    {% if report.summary %}
    <p class="report-card-summary">{{ report.summary }}</p>
    {% endif %}
    {% if report.verdict_counts %}
    <div class="report-card-verdicts">
      {% for verdict, count in report.verdict_counts %}
      <span class="ct-verdict-pill verdict-{{ verdict | replace('partially_supported', 'partial') }}">
        {{ verdict | verdictLabel }}: {{ count }}
      </span>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}
    <span class="report-card-count">{{ report.claim_count }} fullyrðingar</span>
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
{% else %}
<p>Engar greiningar hafa verið birtar ennþá.</p>
{% endif %}
